    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours condition. This specimen is powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system that has been professionally shimmed for optimal timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with high-modulus epoxy and plates. The suspension geometry remains precise, benefiting from fresh bushings and Bilstein PSS10 adjustable dampers. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been scrutinized and serviced. This is a turn-key enthusiast vehicle with zero fluid seepage and a flawless factory finish.",
